NOTE 20  EMPLOYEE STOCK AND SAVINGS PLANS

WE GRANT STOCK-BASED COMPENSATION TO DIRECTORS AND EMPLOYEES. AT JUNE 30, 2011, AN AGGREGATE OF 583 MILLION SHARES WERE AUTHORIZED FOR

