SHARES GENERALLY BECOME AVAILABLE FOR ISSUANCE UNDER THE PLANS. WE ISSUE NEW SHARES OF MICROSOFT COMMON STOCK TO SATISFY EXERCISES AND VESTINGS OF AWARDS GRANTED UNDER ALL OF OUR STOCK PLANS.

